{"tid":594500,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家覺唔覺得佛撚好on9?","createTime":"2018-03-16T01:19:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T12:41:23.000Z","uid":79353,"like":9,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"04e47d3d761cbe66e4a7a40e113dffd6d127a38d","tid":594500,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T01:19:22.000Z","msg":"講明先，覺得佛撚on9，唔代表我信耶。<br />\n<br />\n亦都唔好拎佛同耶作比較。<br />\n佛on9與否 vs 耶比佛更on9 是無關係。<br />\n唔通你逼住喺兩舊屎中間揀一舊?<br />\n林奠同689兩隻賤種，你一定要support其中一個?<br />\n<br />\n而家我的main point係佛撚好on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n講返佛撚，fb素食群組有班死佛撚，日日喺度用佛教角度老屈植物冇生命冇感覺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我心諗收皮啦好無，你又知植物真係冇感覺?<br />\n成日覺得自己好慈悲，因為食既食物係植物，無生命無感覺。<br />\n<br />\n我個人認為你唔好拎呢個觀點嚟自high。<br />\n<br />\n個事實係：其實你已經唔食肉，所以你需要食植物先可以生存。點解唔直認其實你係人，你一定要進食，踩住其他生物上，你先可以生存落去? 唔好喺度講埋d咩野 植物不是生命 植物沒有感覺<br />\nOK?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌柒你班死佛撚唔好日日喺度阿彌陀佛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講明先，本post與耶教無任何關係。"},{"pid":"1e1addb950527609772712ccd762fb28e672f7be","tid":594500,"uid":21423,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T01:22:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"12925d22213f7743f032e2444a77105d669cc3ab","tid":594500,"uid":98915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e1addb950527609772712ccd762fb28e672f7be","tid":594500,"uid":21423,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T01:22:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T01:28:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df464eccaba4cdfbc5f86e88d9a155f3634cbb5b","tid":594500,"uid":101894,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T01:31:57.000Z","msg":"佛觀一缽水 八萬四千蟲<br />\n<br />\n佛睇萬物都係平等 植物都一樣有生命<br />\n只係依家變到好多素食者好似你講咁 屈植物無生命<br />\n食素就企哂係道德高地<br />\n<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c28b8fdbf3c92769dc1458fbea37d73883d713","tid":594500,"uid":79353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T05:59:57.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"69c0ea79c96f5ed7ad569afb9facbc8302b1f121","tid":594500,"uid":90863,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T06:05:11.000Z","msg":"喂阿哥<br />\n啲素食撚借佛教講歪理咁都係素食撚on9啫<br />\n有人借你個名出去殺人放火咁又可以賴落你度？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f20f7460338614850e0e09eed68b417e20ca2f","tid":594500,"uid":136662,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T06:09:24.000Z","msg":"佛撚，又名積分撚，以功德為名去幫自己儲分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c62f1837fbab464cc59be431e9205d9706d21492","tid":594500,"uid":79353,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"89f20f7460338614850e0e09eed68b417e20ca2f","tid":594500,"uid":136662,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T06:09:24.000Z","msg":"佛撚，又名積分撚，以功德為名去幫自己儲分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T09:56:24.000Z","msg":"佢地想儲分打爆六道輪迴game <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/a